Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Knowledge Fusion Module Stub
Provides comprehensive knowledge fusion algorithms and multi-source integration
Enables conflict resolution, consensus building, and unified knowledge representation
:End Note

Type KnowledgeFusionSystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    fusion_paradigm as String
    fusion_engines as List[FusionEngine]
    conflict_resolvers as List[ConflictResolver]
    consensus_builders as List[ConsensusBuilder]
    quality_aggregators as List[QualityAggregator]
    uncertainty_handlers as List[UncertaintyHandler]
    integration_strategies as List[IntegrationStrategy]
    system_configuration as SystemConfiguration

Type FusionEngine is Dictionary with:
    engine_id as String
    engine_type as String
    fusion_algorithms as List[FusionAlgorithm]
    source_rankers as List[SourceRanker]
    evidence_aggregators as List[EvidenceAggregator]
    uncertainty_quantifiers as List[UncertaintyQuantifier]
    confidence_estimators as List[ConfidenceEstimator]
    performance_metrics as PerformanceMetrics
    engine_configuration as EngineConfiguration

Type ConflictResolver is Dictionary with:
    resolver_id as String
    resolution_strategy as String
    conflict_detection as ConflictDetection
    resolution_algorithms as List[ResolutionAlgorithm]
    arbitration_mechanisms as List[ArbitrationMechanism]
    consistency_checkers as List[ConsistencyChecker]
    resolution_metrics as ResolutionMetrics
    resolver_configuration as ResolverConfiguration

Type ConsensusBuilder is Dictionary with:
    builder_id as String
    consensus_mechanism as String
    consensus_algorithms as List[ConsensusAlgorithm]
    agreement_measures as List[AgreementMeasure]
    convergence_criteria as List[ConvergenceCriterion]
    feedback_mechanisms as List[FeedbackMechanism]
    consensus_validation as ConsensusValidation
    consensus_quality as ConsensusQuality

Type FusionAlgorithm is Dictionary with:
    algorithm_id as String
    algorithm_name as String
    algorithm_type as String
    algorithm_implementation as AlgorithmImplementation
    fusion_parameters as FusionParameters
    source_requirements as SourceRequirements
    output_characteristics as OutputCharacteristics
    computational_complexity as ComputationalComplexity

Type KnowledgeSource is Dictionary with:
    source_id as String
    source_name as String
    source_type as String
    source_reliability as Float
    source_authority as Float
    source_freshness as Float
    source_coverage as SourceCoverage
    source_bias as SourceBias
    source_provenance as SourceProvenance
    source_quality as SourceQuality

Type FusedKnowledge is Dictionary with:
    fused_knowledge_id as String
    fusion_method as String
    source_knowledge as List[SourceKnowledge]
    fusion_confidence as Float
    consensus_level as Float
    conflict_resolution as ConflictResolution
    uncertainty_estimation as UncertaintyEstimation
    quality_assessment as QualityAssessment
    provenance_tracking as ProvenanceTracking

Type ConflictDetection is Dictionary with:
    detection_id as String
    conflict_types as List[String]
    detection_algorithms as List[DetectionAlgorithm]
    conflict_patterns as List[ConflictPattern]
    severity_assessment as SeverityAssessment
    conflict_categorization as ConflictCategorization
    detection_metrics as DetectionMetrics

Type EvidenceAggregation is Dictionary with:
    aggregation_id as String
    aggregation_method as String
    evidence_sources as List[EvidenceSource]
    evidence_weights as EvidenceWeights
    aggregation_rules as List[AggregationRule]
    uncertainty_propagation as UncertaintyPropagation
    aggregation_quality as AggregationQuality

Type UncertaintyHandler is Dictionary with:
    handler_id as String
    uncertainty_types as List[String]
    uncertainty_models as List[UncertaintyModel]
    uncertainty_propagation as UncertaintyPropagation
    confidence_estimation as ConfidenceEstimation
    risk_assessment as RiskAssessment
    handler_configuration as HandlerConfiguration

Process called "create_knowledge_fusion_system" that takes fusion_config as Dictionary returns KnowledgeFusionSystem
Process called "fuse_knowledge_sources" that takes fusion_system as KnowledgeFusionSystem and fusion_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_incremental_knowledge_fusion" that takes fusion_system as KnowledgeFusionSystem and incremental_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_temporal_knowledge_fusion" that takes fusion_system as KnowledgeFusionSystem and temporal_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "validate_fusion_quality" that takes fusion_system as KnowledgeFusionSystem and fusion_result as Dictionary and quality_requirements as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "create_knowledge_fusion_monitoring_system" that takes configuration as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_knowledge_fusion_analysis" that takes system as Dictionary and query as Dictionary returns Dictionary 